A Nigerian family leaves the country via OR Tambo International Airport on 11 September 2019 following attacks on foreign nationals. Foreign nationals seek refuge in a Katlehong community hall 10 September 2019. They say they're too scared to stay in their homes for fear of being targeted. The ANCWL's Bathabile Dlamini at the Nicholas Ninow rape trial 11 September 2019. Two unidentified women speak to Dros child rapist Nicholas Ninow ahead of court proceedings on 11 September 2019. The 8-year-old girl and her mother testified in camera. eNCA Reporter Justin Ford speaks to Chester Williams wife and daughter ahead of the Springbok legend's memorial service on 11 September 2019.